rows.label: tlk42100121_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Takaka has realized something, mo!
This is a discovery of the century, mo!

rows.label: tlk42100121_02_msg0002
rows.name:
The height of the Cloud Sea is changing, mo!
If you watch closely, you'll notice it's completely different, mo!

rows.label: tlk42100121_02_msg0003
rows.name:
You go to sleep at night and wake up in the morning,
and it's changed drastically, mo!

rows.label: tlk42100121_02_msg0004
rows.name:
No wonder there are places Takaka used to be able
to go that are now unreachable, mo!

rows.label: tlk42100121_02_msg0005
rows.name:
This discovery is surely award-worthy, mo!
Takaka is going to be famous, mo!
Mofufu~n!
